A short while ago I witnessed your family enter Kaladim to lay waste to the King and many of his guards there. You were all having a fun time doing it too! At the time I was a kitty shaman watching the show, using some pitiful buffs on some of the fighters there. Still, I struck by how much fun you were all seeming to have in carrying out the time honored tradition of  ' Down with Shorty! '<br>
<br>
Being a shaman just wasn't for me, I discovered. I also discovered I had an intense hatred of dwarves, spurred on by the honorless paladin Ggar. So, I recalled myself into a different form and became a Tier'Dal Magician.<br>
<br>
I turned 30 yesterday, and am moving ahead full steam with going for more. This is my main character on the server, and I have no other guises on any of the other servers. I live on the West Coast and have some pretty open hours. So, I'd like the chance to be considered to join you! I've met one of your Necromancers already and fought at his side in Luclin, so I'm pretty sure that you're the kind of people I'd be happiest being with.<br>
<br>
Thanks!<br>
<br>
Shaylee<br>
Magician of the 30th encumbered pet<br>
<br>
